Body:
AND, INDEED, We have set up in the heavens great
			constellations,<span class='fn'>15</span> and endowed them with beauty for all
			to behold;

for, behold, it is We - We alone - who grant life and deal death,
			and it is We alone who shall remain after all else will have
			passed away!<span class='fn'>22</span>

And lo! Thy Sustainer said unto the angels: "Behold, I am about
			to create mortal man out of sounding clay, out of dark slime
			transmuted;
